  "title": "Power cuts for 18th, 19th and 20th approved",
  "body_lines": [
    "COLOMBO (News 1st); CEB request for 4 hours & 20 minutes power cut due to unavailability of fuel for thermal power plants, approved by PUCSL for Monday (18) and for 4 hours & 50 minutes power cut on Tuesday (19) and Wednesday (20);",
    "3 hours from 9am to 6pm and 1 hour & 20 minutes from 6pm to 10pm.",
    "3 hours & 20 minutes from 8am to 6pm and 1 hour & 30 minutes from 6pm to 10:30pm."
